      • copyUncommonFields

        public static LoaderoModel copyUncommonFields​(LoaderoModel currentObj,
                                              LoaderoModel newObject,
                                              LoaderoModelType type)
        Compares two LoaderModel objects field by field and copies field's values from currentObj into newObject if there are any differences detected. Does nothing if field's values are the same. Slightly modified version of code from SO: https://stackoverflow.com/a/20366149.
        Parameters:
        currentObj - LoaderoModel to compare against.
        newObject - LoaderoModel to be compared.
        type - concrete type of objects to be compared.
        Returns:
        new concrete LoaderoModel object.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if any of provided arguments are null.
        IllegalArgumentException - if Reflection API couldn't get value from the Field.
